name: Elaina (Majo no Tabitabi) LORA
description:
This LoRAs are to be used with their original danbooru tag which is elaina_(majo_no_tabitabi) or elaina_\(majo_no_tabitabi\). Also can be used with other LORA. You need to describe how you want her, as the lora is not overfitted as sometimes it will generate images with different outfits and hair color. If the image is weird, try lowering the weight.

Version 2 is out which I personally prefer more. Feel me to credit me and leave feedbacks on what I can improve on!
